properties.name: text
properties.value: WINSTON! This is Commander Simon speaking. The war on the Dino Dogs is underway!

properties.name: text
properties.value: Get to the end of the city to win the battle and BOOST YOUR SCORE!

properties.name: text
properties.value: This isn't Winston's World. It never was.

properties.name: text
properties.value: You helped us kill all these pesky Dino Dogs though, and that was all we needed.

properties.name: text
properties.value: We knew you would follow those rules whether you wanted to or not. Who did you think was in CONTROL here?

properties.name: text
properties.value: You can probably tell by now that there 's nothing keeping track of your score.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Anyways, press one of these buttons. They both do the same thing. They'll both destroy this gross city with you still in it.

properties.name: messageText
properties.value: Good boy. See you on the other side.
